caption: A woman stands by the serene shoreline as the gentle breeze playfully lifts her long, flowing hair, causing it to dance gracefully in the wind. The soft hues of the sunset paint the sky in pastel shades, casting a warm glow over the tranquil scene. Her silhouette is framed against the calm waters, creating a moment of peaceful reflection and natural beauty.
